Introduction

Jo Ga Bin (previously known as Jo So Jin or Sojin) is a South Korean actress and former singer and rapper currently under Leaders Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group 9MUSES and the trio Nasty Nasty.

After the group's disbandment, she signed as an actress with SE M&M while also holding lessons as a dance teacher under the name Jo So Jin. On March 8, 2021, she announced via Instagram she had legally changed her name to Jo Ga Bin, which she will be using for future acting activities.
